::CyberShark::

    He followed Volois inside. He really had no clue as to what was going to 
happen next, but\ the complex looked amazing. A little ways into the complex 
he heard Magmatron calling to him again, he was getting stronger in his 
calls. CyberShark would have to try and keep up, but each call was more 
powerful than the last, it was getting hard to resist. Maybe Battera would 
help.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
::Wolveritron::

    He finally came across the Maximal base, after tireless hours of walking, 
and some short busts of flight. (Minimal flight power, just enough for really 
big jumps) He had crossed something that would later be called the Grand 
Canyon, but now it was mearly a river.
    He hid in the bushes around the Maximals base, watching waiting. He 
wanted to see what kinds of animals there were in the Maximal base...
